[% WRAPPER layout.tt title="Community" handlesLayout=1 %]

<div class="page-title">
  <h1>Community</h1>
</div>

<section class="community-description">
  <p>Nix and NixOS are developed and used by a diverse and welcoming community
    from all around the world.</p>
</section>

<section class="community-banner clickable-whole">
  <p>Check out what the community has made recently in the <a href="https://weekly.nixos.org/">NixOS Weekly</a>
    newsletter.</p>
</section>

<section class="community-communication">
  <h1>Where to talk?</h1>
  <div>
    <div>
      <h2>Forum</h2>
      <p>The official forum is the right place to get help from other users and
        discuss the development of the projects. There are also Announcements,
        Job offers and Events.</p>
      <div>
        <a class="button" href="https://discourse.nixos.org/">Discourse Forum</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2>Chat</h2>
      <p>Another place to get in contact with other users is the official IRC
        channel:</p>
      <p><a href="irc://irc.freenode.net/#nixos">#nixos</a> on the <a href="https://freenode.net/">freenode network</a>
        (<a href="https://logs.nix.samueldr.com/nixos/">logs</a> are
        available)</p>
      <div>
        <a class="button" href="https://webchat.freenode.net/#nixos">Open Webchat</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2>Unofficial Platforms</h2>
      <p>The community is also active on other platforms.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/NixOS/">reddit</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://discord.gg/RbvHtGa">Discord</a></li>
        <li>stackoverflow: see tags <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/nix">nix</a>, <a
            href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/nixos">nixos</a>, <a
            href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/nixops">nixops</a> and <a
            href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/nixpkgs">nixpkgs</a></li>
        <li>Twitter: see the hashtag <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/NixOS">#nixos</a> (#nix is too ambiguous)</li>
        <li>Mastodon/Fediverse: see the hashtag <a href="https://mastodon.social/tags/nixos">#nixos</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

